3.title: TEST POST
3.description:
Are you passionate about crafting out-of-this-world stories? Join our intergalactic media startup as a Junior Cosmic Content Creator! You'll create engaging blog posts, social media content, and video scripts about space exploration, alien cultures, and futuristic tech for our growing audience across the Milky Way. No rocket science degree needed—just a creative mind and a love for the cosmos!
Freelancer Requirements:

Experience Level: Junior (1-2 years of content creation experience)
Portfolio Link: Share a link to your blog, Medium, or similar platform
Specific Skills/Tools: Proficiency in Canva, Google Docs, and basic video editing (e.g., Adobe Premiere or CapCut)
Availability: 20-30 hours per week
Timezone/Region: Any (must be available for weekly holo-meetings in Galactic Standard Time)
